{"about_the_game":"AIR WARS is a flight simulation game that allows you to become the protagonist in a conflict between countries that actually occurred based on the history of air warfare.<br><br>You will experience an immersive experience through missions suited to actual battles based on the interests between countries that occurred after the actual World War II. You become the ace that all nations seek and participate in an air battle. Survive and continue your fame in this fierce air battle.<br><br>It supports most VR hardware, and after boarding the fighter, you can control the aircraft using the throttle and steering wheel in the virtual cockpit via sticks and controllers. Unleash the hidden instincts of Ace in dire situations and win the battle.<br><br>You can check various information about the game through the Discord channel.<br><br><strong><u>Key Features : </u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/\uac8c\uc784\ud2b9\uc9d5--1.png?t=1723603756\" /><li> Reflects real-world war history<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/\uac8c\uc784\ud2b9\uc9d5--2.png?t=1723603756\" /><br></li><li> Map structure reflects real-world terrain<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/\uac8c\uc784\ud2b9\uc9d5--3.png?t=1723603756\" /><br></li><li> Aircraft implementation based on actual data<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/\uac8c\uc784\ud2b9\uc9d5--4.png?t=1723603756\" /><br></li><li> Supports multiple VR devices</li></ul><br><br><br><u><strong>[Mission list &amp; Aircraft]</strong></u><br><br><strong>a. AIR SCOUT</strong><br>The goal is to complete the given course by participating in air racing on Dokdo, Korea.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/AIR-SCOUT.png?t=1723603756\" /><br><br><strong>b. DOVE OF BOYRA</strong><br>You can experience the battle over Boira, arising from the conflict between Pakistan and India.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/DOVE-OF-BOYRA.png?t=1723603756\" /><br><br><strong>c. BLIZZARD</strong><br>You can experience an air battle in the Falklands area during the British and Argentine wars.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/BLIZZARD.png?t=1723603756\" /><br><br><strong>d. DRUG STORE</strong><br>You can experience an air battle between Syria and Israel in the Beka Valley.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/DRUG-STORE.png?t=1723603756\" /><br><br><strong>e. ALONE FESTIVAL</strong><br>Experience the Georgia-Russian air battle in the Caucasus Mountains.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/ALONE-FESTIVAL.png?t=1723603756\" /><br><br><strong>f. FREEDOM OF AIRWAY</strong><br>You become a pilot for an air show held in Paris, and you can see the flies in a plane that automatically flies along a defined route.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210930/extras/FREEDOM-OF-AIRWAY.png?t=1723603756\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Sky Racer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1210930/ce0911309432792e35dbe2b95c755c514d5aa6fe.jpg"},{"name":"MIG-21 Ace","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1210930/be289faead8754acfade4a11addc01bc17462689.jpg"},{"name":"F86 Ace","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1210930/608b6da066d68a5bf72ee